    "본문HTML": "<p>\n\n</p><p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 17px;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 돋움;\">국제처 글로벌학생팀에서는 외국인 유학생 지원 업무를 함께 할 </span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 돋움;\">국가근로 장학생을 추가 모집하오니, 관심 있는 학생들의 많은 지원 바랍니다.</span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 17px;'> </p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 17px;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 돋움;\">1. 모집 인원 : ○명</span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 17px;'> </p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 17px;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 돋움;\">2. 지원 자격</span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 17px;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 돋움;\">  가. 한국학생 요건</span></span></p>\n<p style='box-siz